sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Wallet
    participant SDK
    participant TinyCloud Node

    User->>SDK: signIn()
    SDK->>Wallet: Request signature (SIWE + ReCap)
    Wallet->>User: Approve & sign
    User->>Wallet: Confirm
    Wallet->>SDK: Signature
    SDK->>TinyCloud Node: Submit signature + session key
    TinyCloud Node->>SDK: Session established
    SDK->>User: Ready
